<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٢٠٧٥ - <span class="c4">[ركن]</span> لقب إمام الصّيّادىّ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مذكور فى <span class="c2">«القنية»</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
